{
  "stem": "3855.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When you go to Slovenia and Croatia and Yugoslavia, you will see all the big buildings painted yellow date from the Austrian monarchy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They have been taken over by Tito and made into old age homes, et cetera, and government offices.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There is very little new there, except magnificent hotels for tourism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went into this battle in Poland, even though he was of Czech extraction.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was injured there and was nursed back to health by a Polish woman-- what is referred to in Polish szlachta, which means of noble blood.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was a Christian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they fell in love, and they got married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And even though my grandfather was, I wouldn't call it reformed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no such thing in those days, but he was very progressive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He, if you know the very famous paintings, broke the sticks over his son.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he didn't rend his clothing, but he said, you're finished.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the whole family ostracized him for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he made a career there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He became what was referred to as the district physician, supervising government edicts and general health control, in addition to having his private practice.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the lady in question, with a mother who was a piano virtuoso, passed away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And here he was in this little town, in [INAUDIBLE] in Poland, with no relatives, nobody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All by himself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he had kept up the friendship with my mother and father, because there he studied and there was a different bond.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so he wrote my mother to send him somebody to spend the summer with him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was this opportunity to get me to become a doctor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she sent me there immediately.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
